event.title: SSC MTS exam results 2017
event.description:
SSC MTS 2017 Result Date

The Written Exam has been conducted in two Papers. The Paper 1 contains objective type Questions basison General Intelligence and Reasoning, Numerical Aptitude and General English for total nussc-mts-result-2017mber of marks of 200 and the duration of paper was 2 hours. The Paper 2 contains descriptive type questions based on short essay in Hindi and English for 50 marks and duration for 30 Minutes. Now all the candidates are very eager to know SSC Multitasking Staff Exam Result 2017 and they are regular visiting on official website to check latest information.

Read more here: http://www.sscmtsresult2017.in/
